# RankPrompt Agency Copilot — environment

# The copilot connects to RankPrompt over the hosted MCP server (see .mcp.json).
# Preferred auth is OAuth: in Claude Code run `/mcp` and log in via browser — no key needed here.
#
# Optional: pass-through API key fallback (if you prefer a key over OAuth, or for headless use).
# Create one at https://app.rankprompt.com/developers (needs an API plan). Shown only once.
# RANKPROMPT_API_KEY=rp_live_xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx

# Requires a RankPrompt Starter plan or higher.
